Summary: I took a photo of storm clouds when I looked at photo in the camera I saw UFO, not visible when I took photo!!
trends: There have been no other sightings in Villaverde del Río
This sighting has never been favorited.
divs: Sighting DetailsWe were experiencing a tropical storm with very black clouds so I decided to take some photos as these storms are very rare here.I snapped at the dark clouds and went inside the house to see what the photos looked like.I was amazed to see a UFO in front of the black clouds, It wasnt there when I took the photo !!This is my second sighting this year, the other I imformed you about on 01.01.09. I feel amazed that this has happened twice!! The photo I am sending you is the UFO I saw on 01.01.09 and will send the other to you via Google Mail.
